{"word":"Queen","slug":"queen","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Queen</b> The wife of a king<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=19'>1Ki 11:19</a><br/> Crowned<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=1&verse=11'>Est 1:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=2&verse=17'>Est 2:17</a><br/> Divorced<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=1&verse=22'>Est 1:22</a><br/> Sits on the throne with the king<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=2&verse=6'>Neh 2:6</a><br/> Makes feasts for the women of the royal household<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=1&verse=9'>Est 1:9</a><br/> Exerts an evil influence in public affairs<br/> <a href='S:Jezebel'>Jezebel</a><br/> Counsels the king<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=12'>Dan 5:12</a><br/> Of Sheba, visits Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=13'>1Ki 10:13</a><br/> Candace, of Ethiopia<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=27'>Act 8:27</a><br/> The reigning sovereign, Athaliah<br/> <a href='S:Athaliah'>Athaliah</a><br/> The moon called queen of heaven<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=18'>Jer 7:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=44&verse=19'>Jer 44:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=44&verse=25'>Jer 44:25</a><br/> Worshiped<br/> <a href='S:Idolatry'>Idolatry</a>"}]}